    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride and it\u2019s been such a joy to own. It\u2019s in really solid shape and runs like a dream\u2014perfect for anyone looking for a reliable daily driver that still looks great on the road. I\u2019ve taken really good care of it, and I\u2019m sure you\u2019ll love it as much as I have. Let\u2019s get you behind the wheel for a test drive!",
