    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 features the legendary S54 inline-six, delivering linear power through six individual throttle bodies and high-pressure double-VANOS variable valve timing. Mated to a crisp 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and a factory limited-slip differential, the drivetrain remains tight and responsive. Recent preventative maintenance includes rod bearing replacement and rear subframe reinforcement, ensuring structural rigidity under high lateral loads. The chassis retains its factory-tuned damping characteristics, providing the communicative feedback this platform is renowned for. A mechanically sound example of BMW\u2019s high-revving naturally aspirated era, perfect for the purist driver.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 6
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Used car. Good condition. Well-maintained. Clean title. Reliable daily driver. No mechanical issues.",
