    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This meticulously maintained vehicle is the perfect choice for a buyer seeking reliability paired with a premium feel. The exterior finish retains a deep, glossy luster, showing only the minor, superficial character marks consistent with careful use. Inside, the cabin is a pristine, smoke-free environment; the leather seating has been regularly conditioned to prevent wear, and the wood-grain accents remain vibrant. Every feature, from the responsive touchscreen infotainment system to the dual-zone climate control, operates exactly as intended. Under the hood, the engine is clean and runs whisper-quiet, backed by a comprehensive service log showing on-time oil changes and preventative maintenance. The tires have ample tread remaining, and the brakes feel firm and responsive. This car has been driven with respect and is ready to provide its next owner with years of dependable service.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
