    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m looking to find a new home for my trusty car, and it\u2019s been such a joy to own! It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super dependable for all my daily commutes and weekend trips. It drives smoothly, looks great, and is totally ready for its next adventure with you. If you\u2019re looking for a reliable ride that\u2019s been well-loved, this is definitely the one! Feel free to reach out if you have any questions or want to take it for a spin!",
      "price": 33500.0,
