    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available for the discerning driver is this E46-generation M3, powered by the high-revving S54B32 inline-six featuring individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS variable valve timing system. This example features the sought-after Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox, providing a direct mechanical connection to the rear-mounted limited-slip differential. The chassis has been vetted with recent subframe reinforcement and a full cooling system overhaul. While the exterior and interior exhibit the honest patina of a well-loved driver, the powertrain remains robust, delivering linear acceleration up to its 8,000 RPM redline. Suspension components have been maintained to preserve the car's legendary 50/50 weight distribution and sharp turn-in characteristics.",
